    "DisplayTitle": "Rookie Hauler Needed for Large Shipment",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nCFP has an urgent request for a pilot with combat experience. A few of their settlements are under immediate threat and may soon be under attack, so they need supplies ASAP. \n\nIf you're confident that you can navigate a potential combat zone, please head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>, grab the cargo, and bring it to these locations:\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)\n\nYou'll need enough room for <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>, and your own <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded and unloaded.\n\nKeep in mind that it's always best to run if someone tries to ambush you. But if you get cornered, don't hesitate to defend yourself.",
    "DescriptionKey": "RedWind_HaulCargo_SingleToMulti_desc_ToCFP_Danger_Timed",
    "DisplayDescription": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nCFP has an urgent request for a pilot with combat experience. A few of their settlements are under immediate threat and may soon be under attack, so they need supplies ASAP. \n\nIf you're confident that you can navigate a potential combat zone, please head to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>, grab the cargo, and bring it to these locations:\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination1|Address]</EM4>\n\nYou'll need enough room for <EM4>16 SCU cargo containers</EM4>, and your own <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded and unloaded.\n\nKeep in mind that it's always best to run if someone tries to ambush you. But if you get cornered, don't hesitate to defend yourself.",
